      <p begin="02:28.620" end="02:30.750" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="02:28.620" end="02:28.980">寂</span><span begin="02:28.980" end="02:29.160">し</span><span begin="02:29.160" end="02:29.360">く</span><span begin="02:29.360" end="02:29.490">な</span><span begin="02:29.490" end="02:29.660">い</span><span begin="02:29.660" end="02:29.810">よ</span><span begin="02:29.810" end="02:30.130">今</span><span begin="02:30.130" end="02:30.460">更</span><span begin="02:30.570" end="02:30.750">もう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经不寂寞了哦 事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sabishikunai yo imasara mou</span></p>
