      <p begin="02:33.610" end="02:38.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="02:33.610" end="02:33.780">だ</span><span begin="02:33.780" end="02:33.930">か</span><span begin="02:33.930" end="02:34.040">ら</span><span begin="02:34.160" end="02:34.310">も</span><span begin="02:34.310" end="02:34.460">う</span><span begin="02:36.330" end="02:36.510">テ</span><span begin="02:36.510" end="02:36.670">レ</span><span begin="02:36.670" end="02:36.840">パ</span><span begin="02:36.840" end="02:37.180">シー</span><span begin="02:37.180" end="02:37.330">に</span><span begin="02:37.330" end="02:37.500">気</span><span begin="02:37.500" end="02:37.650">づ</span><span begin="02:37.650" end="02:37.850">い</span><span begin="02:37.850" end="02:38.010">た</span><span begin="02:38.010" end="02:38.210">振</span><span begin="02:38.210" end="02:38.370">り</span><span begin="02:38.370" end="02:38.520">し</span><span begin="02:38.520" end="02:38.720">て</span><span begin="02:38.720" end="02:38.880">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以就装作已经察觉到了心灵感应吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara mou terepashii ni kizuita furi shite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:39.020" end="02:41.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="02:39.020" end="02:39.260">そ</span><span begin="02:39.260" end="02:39.410">の</span><span begin="02:39.410" end="02:39.570">目</span><span begin="02:39.570" end="02:39.740">か</span><span begin="02:39.740" end="02:39.900">っ</span><span begin="02:39.900" end="02:40.090">ぽ</span><span begin="02:40.090" end="02:40.260">じ</span><span begin="02:40.260" end="02:40.420">っ</span><span begin="02:40.420" end="02:40.580">て</span><span begin="02:40.580" end="02:40.740">気</span><span begin="02:40.740" end="02:41.090">づ</span><span begin="02:41.090" end="02:41.280">い</span><span begin="02:41.280" end="02:41.450">た</span><span begin="02:41.450" end="02:41.830">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你睁大眼睛察觉到了的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me kappojitte kizuitara</span></p>
      <p begin="02:42.120" end="02:45.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="02:42.120" end="02:42.650">心</span><span begin="02:42.650" end="02:42.770">の</span><span begin="02:42.770" end="02:43.090">内</span><span begin="02:43.090" end="02:43.260">を</span><span begin="02:43.260" end="02:43.590">荒</span><span begin="02:43.590" end="02:43.830">ん</span><span begin="02:43.830" end="02:43.940">で</span><span begin="02:44.170" end="02:44.490">送</span><span begin="02:44.490" end="02:44.690">っ</span><span begin="02:44.690" end="02:44.830">て</span><span begin="02:44.830" end="02:45.020">み</span><span begin="02:45.020" end="02:45.180">て</span><span begin="02:45.180" end="02:45.330">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就试着将这荒芜的内心发送过来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no uchi o susande okutte mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:45.530" end="02:46.700" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="02:45.530" end="02:45.700">飛</span><span begin="02:45.700" end="02:45.920">ば</span><span begin="02:45.920" end="02:46.050">し</span><span begin="02:46.050" end="02:46.210">て</span><span begin="02:46.210" end="02:46.380">み</span><span begin="02:46.380" end="02:46.540">て</span><span begin="02:46.540" end="02:46.700">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着让它飞翔吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tobashite mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:46.860" end="02:49.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="02:46.860" end="02:47.070">そ</span><span begin="02:47.070" end="02:47.250">の</span><span begin="02:47.250" end="02:47.570">電</span><span begin="02:47.570" end="02:47.650">波</span><span begin="02:47.650" end="02:47.730">思</span><span begin="02:47.730" end="02:48.100">考</span><span begin="02:48.100" end="02:48.220">で</span><span begin="02:48.220" end="02:48.650">叫</span><span begin="02:48.650" end="02:48.780">ん</span><span begin="02:48.780" end="02:48.950">で</span><span begin="02:48.950" end="02:49.120">み</span><span begin="02:49.120" end="02:49.250">て</span><span begin="02:49.250" end="02:49.400">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着用那电波思考呼喊吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono denpa shikou de sakende mite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:49.640" end="02:52.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="02:49.640" end="02:49.800">で</span><span begin="02:49.800" end="02:49.970">き</span><span begin="02:49.970" end="02:50.120">る</span><span begin="02:50.120" end="02:50.310">な</span><span begin="02:50.310" end="02:50.470">ら</span><span begin="02:50.470" end="02:50.830">今</span><span begin="02:50.830" end="02:50.970">も</span><span begin="02:50.970" end="02:51.320">笑</span><span begin="02:51.320" end="02:51.500">っ</span><span begin="02:51.500" end="02:51.840">て</span><span begin="02:51.840" end="02:52.020">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果可以的话现在也笑一笑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dekiru nara ima mo waratte yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:52.340" end="02:54.870" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L54"><span begin="02:52.340" end="02:52.550">で</span><span begin="02:52.550" end="02:52.680">も</span><span begin="02:52.680" end="02:53.000">今</span><span begin="02:53.000" end="02:53.200">は</span><span begin="02:53.200" end="02:53.380">記</span><span begin="02:53.380" end="02:53.700">号</span><span begin="02:53.700" end="02:53.860">ば</span><span begin="02:53.860" end="02:54.040">か</span><span begin="02:54.040" end="02:54.230">り</span><span begin="02:54.230" end="02:54.550">で</span><span begin="02:54.550" end="02:54.870">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是即使现在全是符号</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Demo ima wa kigou bakari demo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:55.090" end="02:56.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L55"><span begin="02:55.090" end="02:55.440">愛</span><span begin="02:55.440" end="02:55.600">し</span><span begin="02:55.600" end="02:55.780">て</span><span begin="02:55.780" end="02:55.960">い</span><span begin="02:55.960" end="02:56.100">る</span><span begin="02:56.100" end="02:56.280">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也是爱着你的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aishiteiru no</span></p>
